.TH SUM2 "9" "2025-05-27" "LinuxCNC Documentation" "HAL Component"
.SH NAME

sum2 \- Sum of two inputs (each with a gain) and an offset
.SH SYNOPSIS
.HP
.B loadrt sum2 [count=\fIN\fB|names=\fIname1\fB[,\fIname2...\fB]]
.SH FUNCTIONS
.TP
\fBsum2.\fIN\fB\fR (requires a floating-point thread)

.SH PINS
.TP
.B sum2.\fIN\fB.in0\fR float in \fR
.br
.ns
.TP
.B sum2.\fIN\fB.in1\fR float in \fR
.br
.ns
.TP
.B sum2.\fIN\fB.out\fR float out \fR
out = in0 * gain0 + in1 * gain1 + offset
.SH PARAMETERS
.TP
.B sum2.\fIN\fB.gain0\fR float rw \fR(default: \fI1.0\fR)
.br
.ns
.TP
.B sum2.\fIN\fB.gain1\fR float rw \fR(default: \fI1.0\fR)
.br
.ns
.TP
.B sum2.\fIN\fB.offset\fR float rw \fR
